      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not even about the mental health side of it. it's the logic of it. the work was the foundation of my identity. if the foundation is a lie, then the person who built it doesn't actually exist. there's no \"getting better\" from a total erasure of yourself. it just feels like the performance is over.",
