    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's just noise. people talking about \"relationships\" or \"inner life\" is just trying to paper over the gap. the truth is, once the legacy is gone, there's no real substance left. people are just going to see the error. it feels like there's no point in continuing the charade when the core of everything has been exposed as nothing.",
