    "summary": "The user expresses profound existential despair and a loss of identity following a massive professional failure, suggesting they have \"nothing left to exist for.\" The assistant acknowledges the user's distress and validates the difficulty of the situation but consistently steers the conversation toward finding value in other areas of life and suggests seeking professional support.",
